Products.Description: 10K Rose Engagement Base Mounting
Products.ShortDescription: 12654 / 10K Rose / Base / Polished / Bridal Tulipset
Products.LongGroupDescription:
Elegant, feminine, strong, and secure - Tulipset mountings are for the discriminating, sophisticated customer.The unique tulip-shaped head offers unsurpassed security, as this copyright-protected design effectively provides eight prongs joined at four points for an extremely safe, durable setting. The Tulipset line includes unique engagement ring styles beautifully accented with fancy-cut princess, baguette, or round accents and quality solitaire rings with matching bands.

Diamonds sold separately.

DescriptiveElementGroup.GroupName: Used to replace CIS_30, which used PDS SIZE field
